subsection.def:
approved payment means (認可繳費媒介) means a card or device, or an electronic
                system, approved by the Commissioner under regulation 12A;
                    (25 of 2020 s. 7)

displayed
                    (展示) with respect to a monthly pass means
                displayed in the manner described in paragraph 5 of Schedule 4;

ticket
                    (停車票) means a car park ticket issued in
                accordance with regulation 21;

paragraph.content:
uses or attempts to use, for indicating payment of a parking fee, a display
                    ticket which has been altered, defaced, damaged or otherwise interfered
                    with;

subparagraph.content:
after receiving the notice of cancellation from the Commissioner,
                        immediately ensure that the permit is not displayed on the vehicle;
                        and

subsection.def:
e-permit (電子許可證) means a disabled
                person’s parking permit issued in the form of an electronic record (as defined by
                    section 2(1) of the Electronic Transactions Ordinance (Cap. 553));
